OL,7,FKyle Clifford raped his ex-girlfriend
OL,8,Fin a "violent, sexual act of spite"
OL,9,Fbefore murdering her, her sister with
OL,10,Fa crossbow and stabbing their mother
OL,11,Fto death with a butcher's knife, a
OL,12,Fcourt has heard.
OL,14,FClifford is alleged to have become
OL,15,F"angry" when his 25-year-old former
OL,16,Fpartner Louise Hunt ended their 18-
OL,17,Fmonth relationship before "carefully"
OL,18,Fplanning and executing the murders on
OL,19,FJuly 9, 2024.
