OL,7,FCambridge Crown Court heard that
OL,8,FClifford tricked 61-year-old Carol
OL,9,FHunt, wife of BBC racing commentator
OL,10,FJohn Hunt, into letting him into the
OL,11,Ffamily home before stabbing her to
OL,12,Fdeath in a "brutal knife attack".
OL,14,FAfter killing Carol and Louise, he
OL,15,Ffatally shot 28-year-old Hannah Hunt
OL,16,Fwhen she returned to the family home
OL,17,Fin Ashlyn Close in Bushey,
OL,18,FHertfordshire, after work.
