OL,9,Fprolonged incident of violence, the
OL,10,Fprosecution alleges that the defendant
OL,11,Fraped Louise Hunt.
OL,13,F"It was a violent, sexual act of
OL,14,Fspite, before he then killed her.
OL,16,F"You will have to determine that
OL,17,Fallegation against him."
