OL,7,FThe court heard that customers of
OL,8,FLouise's dog grooming business, based
OL,9,Fin the Hunt family's garden, were
OL,10,Fusing the gate at the side of the
OL,11,Fhouse "not realising" what was
OL,12,Fhappening inside.
OL,14,FAfter the attack, Clifford, who served
OL,15,Fin the military from 2019 for about
OL,16,Fthree years, was subject to a manhunt
OL,17,Ffor several hours before being found
OL,18,Finjured in Lavender Hill Cemetery in
OL,19,FEnfield, north London, after shooting
OL,20,Fhimself in the chest with the crossbow.
