OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FFive days before the murders, Louise
OL,8,Fwrote a note on her phone titled "When
OL,9,Fyou're sad, look," listing concerns
OL,10,Fabout Clifford, including his racism,
OL,11,Fnegative comments about transgender
OL,12,Fpeople, and use of "belittling
OL,13,Flanguage".
OL,15,FProsecutor Ms Morgan said that in the
OL,16,Fdays before the attacks, Clifford
OL,17,Fsearched for crossbows online and
OL,18,Fviewed pornography, including a video
OL,19,Fof ex-HMP Wandsworth officer Linda De
OL,20,FSousa Abreu, who admitted having sex
OL,21,Fwith a prisoner last year.
