OL,7,FMs Morgan said Clifford's violent
OL,8,Fintentions were clear from "his use of
OL,9,Fweapons and his sexual preoccupations".
OL,11,FAddressing the defendant's motive to
OL,12,Fkill his victims, Ms Morgan said:
OL,13,F"Louise instigated the end of the
OL,14,Frelationship, supported by her friends
OL,15,Fand family.
OL,17,F"In the days that followed, the
OL,18,Fmessage prompted the defendant to try
OL,19,Fto rekindle the relationship in
OL,20,Fvarious ways, all of which were
OL,21,Frebuffed by Louise Hunt.
